{"tid":1200763,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真post]識巫術、降頭的師傅麻煩入一入來","createTime":"2019-06-10T22:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T03:22:54.000Z","uid":217558,"like":10,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"88e7ab1ede3bc2c1d05255532d979d86fc9cd39b","tid":1200763,"uid":217558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T22:59:44.000Z","msg":"既然政府可以這樣橫蠻無理，我們有何需要客客氣氣。<br />\n不想流血衝突，可以試試用一些怪力亂神的方法去解決。<br />\n既然耶撚認為唱唱聖詩就可以令柒婆聖靈感召收回承命，我們何不以巫術、降頭接著應戰。<br />\n常言道：「小病是福」，只要有法力高強的師傅作法令五至七個建制狗蒙受祝福，（當然仲要自由黨堅轉軚）表決當日臥病在床，不能出席便能成事。<br />\n此界別的能人異士，可否幫幫忙，若能成事，香港人都會對你們感激不盡。"},{"pid":"bab016763ddf50e0d9cb712c8d008221564690df","tid":1200763,"uid":130177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T23:10:47.000Z","msg":"啱啊 如果真係得我畀一個月糧你又點話<br />\n不過如果真係掂，就唔請殺手啦<br />\n每個國家鬥法就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de361909b3d44e7c7836a2a77210e6646e8f0831","tid":1200763,"uid":55177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T23:11:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f75bc1648488502955cae7be5fb2d298600ca9ed","tid":1200763,"uid":114271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T23:16:10.000Z","msg":"樓豬收集咗佢地頭髮先"},{"pid":"b664814e627fe1612dca7b2b10fd417eea2fae20","tid":1200763,"uid":217558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T23:18:56.000Z","msg":"法力無邊的，只看照片也能施法。（好似係）"},{"pid":"b333036a4238053fb1dc013767d94e91e035a518","tid":1200763,"uid":121504,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T23:20:02.000Z","msg":"中共有大把玄學佬幫佢地都唔出奇"},{"pid":"a3c8f8289593b13bcdb52d70671ecaf5e7f75afc","tid":1200763,"uid":18517,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T23:26:15.000Z","msg":"如果咁勁 唔洗打仗喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48cedf7c97dca6414e514b16039c334c85d9ae8d","tid":1200763,"uid":1334